<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Pharmacy Dashboard</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#f7f9fb] font-sans text-[#333]">

  <nav class="bg-[#007B8A] text-white px-8 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
    <a href="index.html" class="flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-xl transition-colors hover:text-[#ffd700]">
      <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white transition-colors hover:text-[#ffd700]" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 22 22">
        <path d="M12 3l9 8h-3v9h-12v-9h-3l9-8z"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="tracking-wide">Nova</span>
    </a>
    <ul class="flex gap-6 font-medium">
      <li><a href="/doctors" class="hover:text-[#ffd700]">Doctors</a></li>
      <li><a href="/patients" class="hover:text-[#ffd700]">Patients</a></li>
      <li><a href="/pharmaceutical-companies" class="hover:text-[#ffd700]">Pharmaceutical Companies</a></li>
      <li><a href="/drugs" class="hover:text-[#ffd700]">Drugs</a></li>
      <li><a href="/pharmacies" class="hover:text-[#ffd700]">Pharmacies</a></li>
      <li><a href="/prescriptions" class="hover:text-[#ffd700]">Prescriptions</a></li>
      <li><a href="/pharmacy-drugs" class="hover:text-[#ffd700]">Pharmacy Drugs</a></li>
      <li><a href="/pharmacy-contracts" class="hover:text-[#ffd700]">Pharmacy Contracts</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <div class="text-center mt-6">
    <svg class="h-28 w-auto mx-auto" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 300 80">
      <circle cx="60" cy="40" r="36" fill="#ffd700"/>
      <path d="M60 25 v30 M45 40 h30" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <text x="120" y="48" font-family="Segoe UI, sans-serif" font-size="24" font-weight="bold" fill="#004d40">Nova Pharmacy</text>
    </svg>
  </div>

  <main class="grid grid-cols-[repeat(auto-fit,_minmax(250px,_1fr))] gap-8 p-8">
    <a href="/doctors" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer" id="medicines">
      <h3 class="text-[#007B8A] mb-2 text-lg font-semibold">Doctors</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Registered doctors with specialties and experience.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/patients" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer" id="branches">
      <h3 class="text-[#007B8A] mb-2 text-lg font-semibold">Patients</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Stores patient info, including address, age, and assigned doctor.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/pharmaceutical-companies" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer" id="employees">
      <h3 class="text-[#007B8A] mb-2 text-lg font-semibold">Pharmaceutical Companies</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Drug manufacturers collaborating with pharmacies.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/drugs" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer" id="sales">
      <h3 class="text-[#007B8A] mb-2 text-lg font-semibold">Drugs</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Catalog of drugs with brand names and formulas.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/pharmacies" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer" id="medicines">
      <h3 class="text-[#007B8A] mb-2 text-lg font-semibold">Pharmacies</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Details of individual pharmacy branches.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/prescriptions" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer" id="branches">
      <h3 class="text-[#007B8A] mb-2 text-lg font-semibold">Prescriptions</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Records of medications prescribed to patients.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/pharmacy-drugs" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer" id="employees">
      <h3 class="text-[#007B8A] mb-2 text-lg font-semibold">Pharmacy Drugs</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Inventory and pricing of drugs at each pharmacy.</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/pharmacy-contracts" class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-6 rounded-xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition-transform hover:-translate-y-1 cursor-pointer" id="sales">
      <h3 class="text-[#007B8A] mb-2 text-lg font-semibold">Pharmacy Contracts</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Contractual agreements between pharmacies and companies.</p>
    </a>
  </main>

</body>
</html>
